{"tid":25392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個難頂濕鳩同事","createTime":"2016-12-06T05:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T06:23:14.000Z","uid":18667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94c3e8ec448234af794fd48062f898e24a98f848","tid":25392,"uid":18667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:54:40.000Z","msg":"講返條友背景先 ：<br />\n33 歲 ，A0，下面簡稱處男<br />\n<br />\n事原係我見部printer冇晒碳粉，就叫處男換一個新toner入去，咁我就繼續忙我手頭上嘅嘢啦。過左5分鐘，我見處男仲響度玩緊，我就行過去睇下條友搞乜。一行埋去我屌佢老母，成張檯連部printer 都係碳粉，我即刻屌鳩佢：<br />\n<br />\n我：你做過啲咩？呢度發生咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢：⋯⋯⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：換個toner會搞成咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢：⋯⋯⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見佢十問九唔應，我就自己去睇下個 toner 啦，一拎上手，我不禁大聲屌左出聲，屌你老味條柒頭竟然打開新toner個蓋，同我就咁倒碳粉入舊嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要同我倒到周圍都係碳粉，大佬部printer新買㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你唔識換都可以問下人啊，你老味搞到我啱啱俾老細屌到暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家身邊有冇呢類極品同事？分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14aa1609250a4da2d2c4b750650c4a10fbb67b3","tid":25392,"uid":33595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:57:33.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"bf06ecf1ee5bb1541c2f7ea42a4abc026d80403e","tid":25392,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:59:26.000Z","msg":"佢係蠢姐<br />\n唔係濕鳩"},{"pid":"de7db73c20aa9ec2cd61bfcf4a440f11879cd7b8","tid":25392,"uid":21310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:00:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2640917a5ae8b1d8684c74de5d677f84b9323f9","tid":25392,"uid":41353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:01:46.000Z","